These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: azure, light-blue
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, bluemaster
1. the davidoff-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Color   | light-blue | azure |
| Cigar     | bluemaster    | davidoff   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, lily
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, mango
1. the person eating cauliflower is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Flower   | lily | poppy        |
| Food      | cauliflower  | mango |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
House: victorian, futuristic
2 different games are played: backgammon, canasta
1. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
2. the futuristic house is on the left of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| House   | futuristic    | victorian |
| Game   | backgammon | canasta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
2 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, azure
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the person who likes azure is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Game   | chess      | mah-jongg |
| Color       | coral | azure    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
There 2 different types of food: tomato, kale
City: hamburg, new-york
1. the person traveling to hamburg is in an even position##4
2. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Food           | tomato | kale |
| City   | new-york    | hamburg         |

